<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>직원 로그인 - MediCare+</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 relative">
    <a href="/" class="absolute top-8 left-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 font-medium transition-colors">
        <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
        처음으로
    </a>

    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 w-full max-w-md">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 mx-auto mb-4">
                <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">직원 로그인</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">병원 업무 시스템에 접속합니다.</p>
        </div>

        {{#error}}
        <div class="mb-4 p-3 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl text-red-600 text-sm text-center">
            아이디 또는 비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.
        </div>
        {{/error}}

        {{#logout}}
        <div class="mb-4 p-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl text-green-600 text-sm text-center">
            로그아웃되었습니다.
        </div>
        {{/logout}}

        <form action="/login" method="post" class="space-y-6">
            <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">

            <div>
                <label for="username" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">사번 (아이디)</label>
                <div class="relative">
                    <i data-lucide="user" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                    <input
                        id="username"
                        name="username"
                        type="text"
                        required
                        autofocus
                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none"
                        placeholder="사번을 입력하세요"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">비밀번호</label>
                <div class="relative">
                    <i data-lucide="lock" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                    <input
                        id="password"
                        name="password"
                        type="password"
                        required
                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none"
                        placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <button
                type="submit"
                class="w-full py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-xl font-medium text-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm"
            >
                로그인
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
